<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.6.9">
<l>niṉṟa viṉaiyun tuyaruṅ keṭamā malarēnti</l>
<l>ceṉṟu paṇimi ṉeḻumiṉ toḻumiṉ toṇṭīrkāḷ</l>
<l>eṉṟu miravum pakalum varivaṇ ṭicaipāṭa</l>
<l>kuṉṟiṉ mullai maṉṟiṭai nāṟuṅ kuṟuṅkuṭiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>So that sorrows and persisting karma are destroyed,</l>
<l>Bearing great flowers, come bow. Devotees, arise and worship in Kuṟuṅkuṭi,</l>
<l>Where mountain jasmine scents inner courtyards,</l>
<l>As striped bees always sing songs, night and day.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
